// The commands used by specific applications are listed here by context and Speech Recongition application, 
// and then by OS and receiving/active application and then by colloquial name,
// at this GitHub Repository: https://github.com/auwsome/Commands
// The list here represents the 'consensus' usage of each term per application. Collisions or conflicts can be 
// disputed and resolved by creating an issue for each resolution and voting on it using GitPoll as described in the Read.me

Global Cross OS:
  "Exit" = exit
  "What can I say?" = Commands List
  
  
Windows:
  Global Cross Application:
  
  Windows Speech Recognition:
      General:
        "Start" = Open the Start screen or menu
        Cancel = Cancel the current action or dialog
        Start/stop listening = Turn on/off listening mode
        Move speech recognition = Move the Speech Recognition microphone bar
        Minimize speech recognition = Minimize the microphone bar
        Click File; Start; View = Select any item by its name
        
Click Recycle Bin; Click Computer; Click file name
Select any item or icon

Double-click Recycle Bin; Double-click Computer; Double-click file name
Double tap or double-click any item

Switch to Paint; Switch to WordPad; Switch to program name; Switch application
Switch to an open app

Scroll up; Scroll down; Scroll left; Scroll right
Scroll in one direction

      Keys:
        Press keyboard key; Press a; 
        Press capital b; Press Shift plus a; Press Ctrl plus a
        Delete; Backspace; Enter; Page Up; Page Down; Home; End; Tab = same
      Charms:
        Press Windows Q,S
        Open the Search charm
        Press Windows I
        Open the Settings charm
        Press Windows Z; Right-click
        Show the commands available in the appOperations

Open an app
Open Paint; Open WordPad; Open app name

Switch to an open app
Switch to Paint; Switch to WordPad; Switch to app name; Switch application

Close an app
Close that; Close Paint; Close Documents

Minimize
Minimize that; Minimize Paint; Minimize Documents

Maximize
Maximize that; Maximize Paint; Maximize Documents

Restore
Restore that; Restore Paint; Restore Documents

Cut
Cut that; Cut

Copy
Copy that; Copy

Paste
Paste

Delete
Delete that; Delete

Undo
Undo that; Scratch that; Undo

Scroll in one direction
Scroll up; Scroll down; Scroll right; Scroll left

Scroll an exact distance in pages
Scroll down 2 pages; Scroll up 10 pages

Scroll an exact distance in other units
Scroll up 5; Scroll down 7

Go to a field in a form or an app
Go to field name; Go to Subject; Go to Address; Go to cc

      Sources:
        https://gist.github.com/clojens/9c3e3ff4b7a5535a2575
        http://windows.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-8/using-speech-recognition
      
  Vocola or WSRMacros:
      "Standby" or "Stand By" = cmd Standby 
      
